The Chill CBD Fulfillment Center operates 9-4pm Monday through Friday and 8-12pm on Saturday. Closed Sundays.  All orders processed prior to 12pm will be shipped same day.

Orders originating outside the United States and all other inquiries email info@chill.com. We do not currently ship to Canada.

You will receive an email containing a tracking number once your package has been shipped from our Distribution Center.
